import numpy as np
from matplotlib import pyplot as plt

theta = np.linspace(0, 2*np.pi, 1000)
r = 3* np.sin(8 * theta)
plt.polar(theta+(r<0)*np.pi, np.abs(r), 'r')
plt.show()
